title: This is just too easy! Res Lease in Austin. 2 Beds, 2 Baths
posting_body: ['Check out this gorgeous condo with two bedrooms and two baths in Travis county, Austin, TX, waiting for you to lease!!', 'This unit features elegant wood flooring, ceiling fans to help cool the house in the hotter Texas months, and modern touches throughout.', 'In addition, the well-designed kitchen boasts ample wood cabinetry with stainless steel appliances perfect for creating home-style meals!!', 'The main bedroom is something you want to see!!', 'With ample space and big windows that allow tons of sunlight, it also features an ensuite bathroom with a nice large shower waiting for you to relax after a long day at work.', 'The community green areas are perfect for exercising or relaxing with ample space and a beautiful green lawn!!', 'Water, wastewater and trash are a flat-rate of $60.00/month', 'Schedule your tour and apply for this home today!', 'It will lease fast.', 'In-person tours are required (no exceptions).', 'All renters are enrolled in the resident benefits package.', '--to set up a viewing--', 'Call/Text/Email ANYTIME!', 'Cristian Argueta', 'show contact info', '(ask for ID# 6810339)', 'All City Real Estate Company', 'Have other properties available....', '(Houses, Duplexes, Apartments, Condos, All Areas)', 'Please be Aware of SCAMS...', 'Do NOT reply to this ad, please call/text for a fast response.', 'Listed By: Benjamin Doherty, Sunroom Rentals Texas, LLC']
